languages.text: "Вот как? Надеюсь, твоя власть, что столь тебе нравится, служит иной цели, чем пустое честолюбие."

traits.locale_text: {n}Кибелла прищуривается на вас.{/n} "Вот как, Эним'{name}? Надеюсь, твоя власть, коей ты столь упиваешься, на самом деле служит иной цели, чем пустое честолюбие."

languages.text: "Is that so? I hope that this power you so cherish serves a purpose other than hollow vanity."
languages.original_text: "Вот как? Надеюсь, твоя власть, что столь тебе нравится, служит иной цели, чем пустое честолюбие."

traits.locale_text: "Truly? I hope your cherished power serves a purpose other than hollow vanity."
"Truly? I hope your cherished power serves a purpose other than hollow vanity."
"Is that so? I hope that this power you so cherish serves a purpose other than hollow vanity."
"Is that so? I hope that this power you so cherish serves a purpose other than hollow vanity."
"Is that so? I hope that this power you so cherish serves a purpose other than hollow vanity."
"Is that so? I hope that this power you so cherish serves a purpose other than hollow vanity."

languages.text: «¿Es eso cierto? Espero que el poder que tanto estima tenga otro propósito, además de satisfacer su vanidad».
languages.original_text: "Is that so? I hope that this power you so cherish serves a purpose other than hollow vanity."

traits.locale_text: «¿Es eso cierto? Espero que el poder que tanto estima tenga otro propósito, además de satisfacer su vanidad».

languages.text: 「そうなの？あなたが大切にしているこの力が、空虚な虚栄心以外の目的に役立つことを祈っているわ」
languages.original_text: "Is that so? I hope that this power you so cherish serves a purpose other than hollow vanity."

traits.locale_text: 「そうなの？あなたが大切にしているこの力が、空虚な虚栄心以外の目的に役立つことを祈っているわ」

languages.text: “是这样吗？我希望你如此珍视的权力并非只能用来满足虚荣，还能用于其他目的。”
languages.original_text: "Is that so? I hope that this power you so cherish serves a purpose other than hollow vanity."

traits.locale_text: “是这样吗？我希望你如此珍视的权力并非只能用来满足虚荣，还能用于其他目的。”

languages.text: "Tatsächlich? Ich hoffe, diese von Euch so geschätzte Macht dient nicht nur hohler Eitelkeit."
languages.original_text: "Is that so? I hope that this power you so cherish serves a purpose other than hollow vanity."

traits.locale_text: "Tatsächlich? Ich hoffe, diese von Euch so geschätzte Macht dient nicht nur hohler Eitelkeit."

languages.text: « Vraiment ? Dans ce cas, j'espère que ce pouvoir que vous chérissez tant sert un objectif autre que la seule vanité. »
languages.original_text: "Is that so? I hope that this power you so cherish serves a purpose other than hollow vanity."

traits.locale_text: « Vraiment ? Dans ce cas, j'espère que ce pouvoir que vous chérissez tant sert un objectif autre que la seule vanité. »

languages.text: "Öyle mi? Umuyorum ki böylesine kıymet verdiğin bu güç, içi boş kibirden farklı bir amaca hizmet eder."
languages.original_text: "Is that so? I hope that this power you so cherish serves a purpose other than hollow vanity."
